@startuml
title Activity Diagram - Return Item
skinparam style strictuml

/' TEXT DESCRIPTION (Steps)
1. Member initiates return and provides the book copy.
2. Librarian scans the copy barcode.
3. System finds the active loan.
4. System closes the loan.
5. System updates the copy status to Available.
6. System checks whether the loan is overdue.
7. If overdue, system calculates and creates a fine.
8. System shows or prints the return receipt.
'/

start
:Initiate return (provide book copy);
:Scan copy barcode;
:Find active Loan;
:Close Loan;
:Update BookCopy status to Available;

if (Overdue?) then (Yes)
  :Calculate fine;
  :Create Fine record;
else (No)
  :No fine;
endif

:Show or print return receipt;
stop
@enduml